name: Rei Ayanami (Mogudan) - Neon Genesis Evangelion
description:
One of the first LORA I decided to make but didn't have the confidence to do. I present to you Rei Ayanami in Mogudan Style. Please if you ever get the chance to support Mogudan do so, so he can keep doing more of his wonderful works. His art is superb enough that i feel some shame by making this LORA but I'd like to think of it more as a tribute than anything else.

Got good results with: <lora:Ayanami_Rei_Mogudan:0.45>, Ayanami_Rei_Mogudan, huge_breasts,

Her most common outfits in the dataset are school_uniform, plugsuit, buruma / gym_uniform, virgin_killer_sweater and wedding_dress.

I added the tag summary(last.txt) to the dataset file if you want to experiment with specific tags.
